{"id": "1313341853139079268", "channel_id": "1313341853139079268", "type": 0, "author_id": "1215324714860281949", "author_name": "147asd", "author_bot": false, "content": "今天的活动新boss为什么可以在血希开大回合内加盾啊？这是机制还是bug啊？如果是机制的话，boss这个叫维度壁障的技能优先级比血希技能高？那血希三启的对策作用就这么水灵灵的没了？", "timestamp": "2024-12-03T03:11:38.500000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1313341853751574528", "filename": "Image_40039943759309.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 165841, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1313341853139079268/1313341853751574528/Image_40039943759309.jpg?ex=6a00a02a&is=69ff4eaa&hm=73dcd2b50feb335ed70b42a888af29c66a4122754e5e24fbd82500dacf061ce9&"}, {"id": "1313341854141648967", "filename": "Screenshot_20241203_110852.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 224393, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1313341853139079268/1313341854141648967/Screenshot_20241203_110852.jpg?ex=6a00a02a&is=69ff4eaa&hm=25ce895a33c40f1153d0a372a2894b3a68a4eea6c5d8290351f31bc68022f187&"}, {"id": "1313341854477062267", "filename": "Image_40038294158693.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 130692, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1313341853139079268/1313341854477062267/Image_40038294158693.jpg?ex=6a00a02a&is=69ff4eaa&hm=bf792d15d555cffa127163d9b17270c496ede20dc23e4e96fdafcac7ccb20868&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1313341853139079268", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3启血希破盾问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1313384073422704690", "channel_id": "1313384073422704690", "type": 0, "author_id": "297715103565086721", "author_name": "_riku_0330_", "author_bot": false, "content": "在活動最新開的關卡遇到的\n不知道是機制還是bug\n\n怪會封印喚醒體\n使用了 艾爾瓦 臨戰體勢 解除喚醒體封印\n狂氣爆發被解除了，但原先在手中的卡牌還是被封印住\n\n原先以為是留在手上的不會被解除\n但後來還有遇到開了詹金的狂氣爆發，生成的 4張布朗出動 依舊會是被封印的狀態\n（這部分沒有錄影到）\n所以來此詢問，先謝謝答覆！", "timestamp": "2024-12-03T05:59:24.600000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1313384073942667304", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20241203_134917.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 4851560, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1313384073422704690/1313384073942667304/Screen_Recording_20241203_134917.mp4?ex=6a00c77c&is=69ff75fc&hm=7fcdb92d5d1ad328c2e3675cfd950f47502e6cd14f9312ba539cc6b1923f19b9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1313384073422704690", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "艾爾瓦解除封印問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
